{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SWEEP is a tactical card game where you unleash explosive damage by skillfully combining card hands, stickers, and items.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sick of random draws?\u00a0Pick the cards you want straight from the deck and use your wisdom to create the best combinations.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/Desktop_2024.12.24_-_21.20.40.02.gif?t=1739513428\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Transform Cards into Bullets and Trigger Chain Reactions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize stickers and items on the cards to trigger an astonishing chain of effects, transforming cards into bullets to unleash devastating damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/Desktop_2024.12.24_-_21.20.40.02_3.gif?t=1739513428\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Clear Your Hand, Seize Control</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you clear your hand, you gain a brand-new turn and double all damage dealt. Keep clearing cards to overpower your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/Desktop_2024.12.24_-_21.20.40.gif?t=1739513428\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">90+ unique items, most of which are continuously enhanced as the game progresses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">18+ stickers that grant additional abilities to cards, such as ignition, critical hits, health recovery, etc.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">48 enemies with various styles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">13 advanced modes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you stack items for massive damage or masterfully play for extra turns, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739513428","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/page.bg.jpg?t=1739513428","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/8603f0dccda1d8a3e1427d745751e0cc81dc8cf3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739513428","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/8603f0dccda1d8a3e1427d745751e0cc81dc8cf3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739513428","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3427040,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SWEEP is a tactical card game where you unleash explosive damage by skillfully combining card hands, stickers, and items.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sick of random draws?\u00a0Pick the cards you want straight from the deck and use your wisdom to create the best combinations.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/Desktop_2024.12.24_-_21.20.40.02.gif?t=1739513428\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Transform Cards into Bullets and Trigger Chain Reactions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize stickers and items on the cards to trigger an astonishing chain of effects, transforming cards into bullets to unleash devastating damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/Desktop_2024.12.24_-_21.20.40.02_3.gif?t=1739513428\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Clear Your Hand, Seize Control</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you cl